{"type": "article", "id": 3547, "title": "MOSCHINO 泰迪熊香水", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-14T08:18:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233003r3ngzLa2VQEPbAKY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款玩具熊吗？可是它的身体上明明写着「This is not a Moschino Toy」。仔细一研究，原来是 MOSCHINO 新任创意总监 Jeremy Scott 上任以来推出的首款香氛「Moschino Toy」。这款泰迪熊造型的香水融合了紫罗兰、胸衣草、杜松与佛手柑以及木材等各式香型调出的一款混合中性调性的香水，小熊脑袋为香水的瓶盖，小熊身体则为香水的瓶身。为了推广这款香水，MOSCHINO 甚至找来了超模 Isabeli Fontana 做广告。也许是因为这一设计太有卖点，才上架没几日，这一售价为 110 美元的香水在 <a href=\"http://www.moschino.com/us/fragrance_cod62000760kb.html\" target=\"_blank\">MOSCHINO 官网</a>已标明销售一空。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233002Bua7qoN9iEjAv0Tx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233002aF80TEUSNeVK46ph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233003U9RPTa5YHd3xCE4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}